snippet.title: RPA Podcast 012 - The Johnny Depp Vs Amber Heard Court Situation..
snippet.description: In this episode we discuss the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard current situation with a suite against a London news paper and him closing his case in court and why we as men need to really pay attention to his case, and the situation we as men can be in with the law (when we have proof of our innocence) and your career when it comes to be accused of domestic violence. Reference video for this discussion; The the Better Bachelor Channel https://youtu.be/gvDnFejQpiE
